# skill: architect-decision-record
# purpose: Create Architecture Decision Record (ADR) for major decisions
# triggers: Architect makes significant architectural decision

## Invocation
```
architect-adr --title "<decision title>" \
    --status <proposed|accepted|rejected|superseded> \
    --context "<context describing the problem>" \
    --decision "<the decision made>" \
    --consequences "<positive and negative consequences>" \
    [--related-task <task-id>]
```

## Output
Creates: `docs/adr/<YYYYMMDD-hhmmss-short-title>.md`

## ADR Template
```markdown
# <YYYYMMDD>: <Short Decision Title>

## Status
<proposed | accepted | rejected | superseded>

## Context
<What is the issue that we're seeing that is motivating this decision? What is the
history or background that led to this point?>

### Problem Statement
<Clear statement of the problem>

### Influencing Factors
- <factor 1>
- <factor 2>

## Decision
<What is the change that we're proposing and/or doing?>

### The Decision
<Clear statement of the decision>

### Implementation Details
<How will this be implemented?>

## Consequences
<What becomes easier or more difficult to do because of this decision?>

### Positive Consequences
- <benefit 1>
- <benefit 2>

### Negative Consequences
- <risk/drawback 1>
- <risk/drawback 2>

## Alternatives Considered
1. <alternative 1>
   - <why not chosen>
2. <alternative 2>
   - <why not chosen>

## References
- [Related task](<link>)
- [Related PR](<link>)
- <external references>
```

## Usage Example
```bash
architect-adr \
    --title "Use PostgreSQL for session storage" \
    --status proposed \
    --context "Current in-memory session storage does not support horizontal scaling. Multiple instances cannot share sessions." \
    --decision "Migrate to PostgreSQL-backed session storage with connection pooling" \
    --consequences "Positive: Horizontal scaling enabled, sessions persist across restarts. Negative: Added dependency on PostgreSQL, added latency for session operations." \
    --related-task task-001
```

## Auto-generated Checkpoint
```bash
checkpoint --phase plan --description "ADR created: $TITLE" \
    --next "Awaiting architect approval before implementation"
```
